text: Perched on Buchanan Hill, this single story home offers incredible unobstructed views of the Skagit Valley and Mountains beyond! Step inside to an open living space w/ hardwood floors and gas fireplace. Kitchen has ample cabinet and counter space and an island eating area. Three bedrooms including Primary w/ private en-suite bath and walk in closet. Efficient Heat pump warms or cools the home as needed. Wrap-around covered porch and the back deck is the perfect place to take in those views. Two car garage. Situated on a desirable 1.52 acre lot. Seller offering a $10k credit in lieu of carpet/paint towards buyers closing costs w/ full price offer. 1.52 acre vacant lot next door also for sale MLS# 2297823. You will not want to miss this one!
nearby_schools: Sedro-Woolley School District, Northwest Educational Service District 189

text: Adorable country rambler located in the area of Lyman! Walk through the front door & you are welcomed into the livingroom which features a cozy pellet stove. A dining area can be found as well with a sliding glass door leading to a covered back deck. Two bedrooms & a full bathroom are on one end of the home while the kitchen sits on the other. A bonus room with a wood burning fireplace can be found beside the kitchen which can be used as an office or bedroom if desired. Large laundry room also with access to the garage! Head outside to a spacious back yard complete with a covered patio, chicken coop, & seasonal creek with a bridge! There is a large shop right next to the home, offering ample storage & space for hobbies. Come call it home!

Welcome to this nicely updated Creekside home! Hardwood floors throughout except bedrooms, kitchen and baths. New gas fireplace in 2019 (no pilot needed, remote control), custom window coverings, new windows and slider. Some newer appliances plus washer and dryer. New a/c in 2022. Lots of windows to enjoy a great view of Mount Baker. RV parking onsite. Nice deck off slider. This home has been very well taken care of and is move in ready!

Brand new manufactured home on 1.9 acres close to the Skagit River, Sauk Mountain, and hiking trails (Rockport State Park, Sauk Mountain, and Howard Miller Park). Across the road, you can launch your boat at Howard Miller Park. Property has Full RV hookups plus an APPROVED PERMIT to build a 24 x 36 Shop next to the house. Nice setting with woods surrounding you. Only 35 minutes to Sedro Woolley.

Lovely NW craftsman style cottage home in the beautiful J Avenue Cottages community, a quaint neighborhood that offers pride of ownership and turn key living! This gorgeous home offers main level living, custom woodwork, maple hardwood flooring, vaulted ceilings, & a spacious kitchen with granite counters & stainless appliances. The cozy gas fireplace is perfect for those chilly winter evenings! Spacious primary suite with ensuite bath & walk-in closet. Upstairs has a wonderful sunny loft with views of Mount Baker & Fidalgo bay plus an extra bedroom & full bath for guests. The loft makes a perfect extra family room & office space. Newer ductless mini split heat pump provides A/C on those warmer summer days. Superb in town location!!!

Back on the Market! Escape to your own private oasis with this stunning log cabin, nestled on 4.77 acres of beautifully landscaped land. This property offers a perfect blend of rustic charm and modern convenience, making it an ideal retreat for nature lovers and outdoor enthusiasts. Cozy and inviting, featuring open living spaces, natural wood finishes, and plenty of natural light. Lots of lush greenery, mature trees, fruit trees, and a designated gardening space for your green thumb. The 1680 sq. ft. shop provides ample space for all your tools and toysperfect for hobbies, storage, or a workshop PLUS RV Parking.

Discover your own slice of paradise with this affordable, move-in ready property on 5 acres! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience, featuring a rustic bunkhouse cabin complete with a kitchenette and bathroomideal for guests or as a cozy retreat. The home's floor plan features a split layout with the living space at the heart of the home. Located just minutes from I-5, youll enjoy easy access to both Bellingham and Burlington, while being steps away from Blanchard Mountain trails and endless outdoor recreation. Surrounded by towering evergreens, this private haven provides ample room to relax, explore, and make it your own. Dont miss this unique opportunity for acreage living!
